channel.description: [center][size=24pt]Eclipse-Rsps[/size][/center] [size=8pt]As some of you may know, my last few releases have been apart of the Eclipse-Rsps PvP series. This version however will not be released to the public. I am going to put this online just to see how far it can go ( goal is to have 30 online at one time ). Yes this sounds like a simple goal but i will not be paying for hosting/advertisement. [/size] [size=24pt]The Reason Why[/size] [size=8pt]I am putting this server online because i see to many server's these days that are "pk servers". Back in maybe 2009 or 2008 the deffinition of a pking server was that you PK for your items and that Player Killing was a big part of the server, but that doesnt mean spawn every item and the only thing you can do is PK. I have made the server based on Pking and Skilling for ECP Points. Everytime you level up in a skilling skill ( minning, cooking, fishing, woodcutting, ect. ) you gain 1 ECP. The rates on these skills are 2 though, so it should take fairly long to get a 99 skill. ( roughly 3 hours ). [/size] [size=24pt]The Team Needed[/size] [size=8pt]I will be needing 1.Website Developer 0/1 2.Hoster 0/1 [center][size=14pt]Feature's[[/size]/center] -100% Runecrafting and Rift added. -100% Woodcutting and Firemaking added with new zone - Herblore Skill redone - Smithing 95% - Farming 50-65% - Home - New Slayer challenges - Knight's Assult Minigame added - New boss drop's added - ECT.
